            <title>[CASSANDRA-1850] When the ANTLR code generation fails the build continues and ignores the failure</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1850</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
